  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd 39 \u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "39th Anniversary of Black July Commemoration",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 39th anniversary of the Black July riots against the Tamil people was observed on the 23rd. In the early hours of July 23, 1983, ethnic riots against the Tamil people were unleashed across the country after a landmine attack on the army in Tirunelveli.",
        "During this, thousands of Tamil people from Colombo and other areas were looted and destroyed their properties and were driven northwards as refugees.",
        "Thus commemoration events were conducted in various places on the occasion of the 39th anniversary of Black July when the genocide against Tamils \u200b\u200bwas unleashed.",
        "In this case, advance has been made in Tamil Tesiya Kotalampapu Aluvaikit in Vadamaratsi-Matthadi area. This event is organized by the North Maratshi branch of the Tamil National Federation.",
        "Under the leadership of Member of Parliament MA Sumanthran, members of Provincial Council Municipal Council, Prakadasa Sabha members and members of Vadamaratsi branch took part and lit candles. Meanwhile, the Black July commemoration event was held at the University of Jaffna. In this event, students of Jaffna University paid respects to the memorial, lit lamps and sprinkled flowers.",
        "Also, another event was held at Navalar Mani Mandapam. With the participation of Ananthi Sasitharan and others, an agreement has been reached regarding the formation of a coalition against the destruction of Tamils."
      ],
